"    Baby with cleft lip and baby with cleft palate",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 527px; height: 543px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
