"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/27/3514/abstract/2\">",
"      Dyer JE, Roth B, Hyma BA. Gamma-hydroxybutyrate withdrawal syndrome. Ann Emerg Med 2001; 37:147.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/27/3514/abstract/3\">",
"      Slagel B, Kingstone E, Bhalerao S. Gamma hydroxybutyrate withdrawal in an orthopedic trauma patient. Can J Psychiatry 2003; 48:131.",
"     </a>",
